hopobject.body: I was made redundant two months ago 50 mg topamax side effects Since he was sworn in on Aug. 4, Rouhani has made it clear that he wants to improve relations with the United States and the West.  In addition to conciliatory words, he has taken some concrete steps to show he’s different from his hard-line predecessor, including releasing 11 prominent political prisoners on Wednesday.  He also announced that he would be bringing Iran’s only Jewish lawmaker to New York as part of his official delegation.
